Subject: Wire generated Argo theme into ui-tui

Use the generated Argo theme data as the Ink TUI default so pre-gateway

startup surfaces and theme tests match the shipped CLI skin. Remove the

remaining caduceus/kawaii startup glyphs from Argo-owned TUI status surfaces

without changing the skin-driven fromSkin path.

